{"tid":2451310,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波檯已死，聖安東尼奧30歲先入牙賣加國家隊冇人講？！","createTime":"2021-03-18T04:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:34:10.000Z","uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"92fb7a09394ee3b880d27ea34ef51215c02b5caf","tid":2451310,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"天空體育(Skysports)報導(report)，西咸姆聯(West Ham United)隊前鋒安東尼奧(Antonio)已經決定他的國家隊未來在牙買加(Jamaica)，而不是英格蘭(England)。 上個月(February)，牙買加與這位30歲的球員進行了接觸，之前他一直在考慮(considering)是為他出生的英格蘭國家隊效力，還是為他父母(Parents)出生的加勒比海島嶼(Caribbean Island)踢球。 現在看來這位前鋒已經做出了選擇：代表牙買加隊出場能夠保證更穩定的國際大賽出場時間。"},{"pid":"61bb3bfbdbd48f1e71578e156de4144a012f8880","tid":2451310,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac94b2e047587c70e32e0381e9b71f919b14d2a","tid":2451310,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"你啲括號勁撚迷沙卡）"},{"pid":"150f71f45b5f1f22cec30d346ab24b768ad0d2d7","tid":2451310,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac94b2e047587c70e32e0381e9b71f919b14d2a","tid":2451310,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"你啲括號勁撚迷沙卡）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣冇括<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb33d55a728a56e3a0fbe1f79b66a1acc2b7ae44","tid":2451310,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"正常啦 牙買加前場三叉戠 antonio + andre gray + bailey 勁過英格蘭好撚多"},{"pid":"3a9aeda039d66646bee14505fa508561fa387247","tid":2451310,"uid":54025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"牙賣加隊<br />\n<br />\n 安東尼奧<br />\nLeon Bailey  龍虎切 Sterling"},{"pid":"d6d2cfd7733c3049ceecf8901c8c2369ea852025","tid":2451310,"uid":234509,"li